Package de.chojo.sadu.wrapper.stage

Interface InsertStage

All Superinterfaces:
UpdateStage
All Known Implementing Classes:
QueryBuilder
public interface InsertStage
extends UpdateStage
Represents a InsertStage providing the result of an insert statement.

Can either provide the created keys or a UpdateResult via the underlying UpdateStage
